text = "Project New Dawn's Tower Defence Version 0.0.3 (Alpha)

Controls:
	LMB - Build Tower
	RMB - Cancel Building
	Space - Wave start/Wave slow/Wave 	Speed
	1,2 - Select turret from shop (Only when shop window is opened)
	Q - Open shop window/Close shop window
	R - Rotate turret 90 deg
	Mouse Scroll - rotate turret 1 deg
	,  -  Upgrade path 1
	.  -  Upgrade path 2

Game automatically saves progress when closing with use of Exit button in Main Menu

Web Version serves as a preview and is not recommended."
